snippet.title: Book Review || The Way I Used to Be by Amber Smith
snippet.description:
Book Review || The Way I Used to Be by Amber Smith

SPOILER FREE

I don't think I would have rated this book so highly if I had not identified as much with the main character. Because of that, I was able to disregard a lot of the book's flaws, so I think people who didn't relate as much as I did would be much more conscious of the flaws as they were reading.
